item.title: Help me make a private server! plz i downloaded testscape source wat next?
item.dc:creator: @b1g_th13f b1g th13f
item.description:
@b1g_th13f wrote:

Don’t follow those oh so boring, long ass guide’s.
After you’ve got your source.
Go to http://no-ip.org
create an account.
After you’ve done that, click add on the left hand side of your screen.
Type in a server name of your choice, click add.
Wait 5-10 minutes, and add your server on mopar.
Bingo, you’re done.
